Nanotrasen Station Operations Division
Contraband Possession & Usage Permit
Form Code: AUT-07
Classification: Level 3 – Restricted Authorization

Permit Overview

This document serves as an official authorization for the controlled possession and use of contraband aboard the station under approved conditions. This permit is valid only for the individual named below and is subject to immediate revocation by Command or Security personnel.

Permit Holder Information

Name: ___________________________________________

Rank / Position: _________________________________

Department: _____________________________________

Species: _________________________________________

Identification Number (if applicable): _______________

Contraband Details

Item Description: _________________________________

Serial / Tag (if applicable): ________________________

Approved Purpose of Use: __________________________

Storage Location: _________________________________

Terms and Conditions

The item covered by this permit must not be used in violation of Space Law.

The permit holder assumes full responsibility for the security and use of the item.

Security and Command staff reserve the right to inspect or confiscate the item at any time.

This authorization is void if transferred, duplicated, or used outside approved purposes.

Breach of these terms may result in disciplinary action up to and including execution or demotion, as deemed appropriate by Command.

